    "text": "Exchange Regulatory Improvement Act of 2022\n\nThis bill revises the definition of facility for purposes of regulation under the Securities Exchange Act of 1934. Specifically, the bill provides that a facility does not include any service that can legally be offered by a person or entity that is not a registered exchange."
